<F P=102>   OW1205051294 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0440 
GMT 12 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1205051294 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, 12 May (XINHUA) -- Decree No. 27 of the 
PRC President: 
  According to a decision of the seventh meeting of the Eighth 
National People's Congress Standing Committee of the PRC on 12 
May 1994: 
  1. Zhu Xun has been relieved of his duties as minister of 
geology and mineral resources, and Song Ruixiang has been 
appointed to the post. 
  2. Ai Zhisheng has been relieved of his duties as minister 
of 
radio, cinema, and television, and Sun Jiazheng has been 
appointed to the post. 
  3. Lu Peijian has been relieved of his duties as auditor 
general of the Auditing Administration, and Gu Zhenqian has been 
appointed to the post. 
  [Signed] Jiang Zemin, president of the PRC 
  [Dated] 12 May 1994 

</TEXT>

