<F P=100> NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Political &amp; Social </F>
<H3> <TI>   NPC Standing Committee Removes, Appoints Officials </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    NPC Standing Committee Removes, Appoints Officials </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1205101794 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0506 
GMT 12 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1205101794 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

