  [Text] Beijing, 13 May (XINHUA) -- PRC Presidential Decree 
No. 26: 
  The "Decision of the National People's Congress [NPC] 
Standing Committee on Amendments to the `Regulations Governing 
Officers' Ranks of the Chinese People's Liberation Army [PLA],'" 
approved by the seventh meeting of the Eighth NPC on 12 May 
1994, is hereby promulgated and becomes effective on the day of 
promulgation. 
  [signed] Jiang Zemin, President of the PRC 
  [dated] 12 May 1994 

