<F P=100> United States &amp; Canada </F>
<H3> <TI>   Spokesman Criticizes Planned Lord Meeting With Wang Juntao </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Spokesman Criticizes Planned Lord Meeting With Wang Juntao </PHRASE></F></HT>

